Named after the Quijos region of Napo Province,
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="662336C8FFF7727E8D24FE95FAD01142" blockId="6.[835,1475,265,321]" box="[835,1298,297,321]" pageId="6" pageNumber="295">Ecuador where the specimens were collected.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="2E866543FFF7727E8D05FEE4FAE111B2" pageId="6" pageNumber="295" type="discussion">
